===Etymology===
{{PIE root|en|bʰer}}
From {{inh|en|enm|differren}}, from {{der|en|fro|differer}}, from {{der|en|la|differō||carry apart, put off, defer; differ}}, from {{m|la|dis-||apart}} + {{m|la|ferō||carry, bear}}. Compare {{cog|grc|διαφέρω}}. {{doublet|en|defer}} (etymology 1).

